# ── Privacy firewall ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Tilth is generic-input by design. Provider-specific adapters and any real
# (non-demo) plant data MUST NEVER be committed. The committed repo contains only
# the generic schema, the app, generic importers, and fictional demo data.
data/private/
data/private*.zip
adapters-private/
*.private.json
# Exported backups hold the user's REAL garden (incl. source URLs in sourceLinks) — never commit.
tilth-backup*.json
# Private session handover / notes — local context, never committed.
*.local.md

# ── Build / deps ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
node_modules/
dist/
dist-ssr/
*.local

# ── Env / secrets ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# ── Editor / OS ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
.vscode/*
!.vscode/extensions.json
.idea/
*.log
